08151 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"Paragraph SCXW59908151 BCX8\"\u003e\u003cem\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"EN-NZ\" class=\"TextRun SCXW59908151 BCX8\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW59908151 BCX8\" data-ccp-parastyle=\"p4\" data-ccp-parastyle-defn='{\"ObjectId\":\"b71b86aa-d72c-5c05-bc38-eb0d9113b743|1\",\"ClassId\":1073872969,\"Properties\":[469777841,\"Times New Roman\",469777842,\"Times New Roman\",469777843,\"Times New Roman\",469777844,\"Times New Roman\",469769226,\"Times New Roman\",268442635,\"24\",335559705,\"2057\",335551547,\"5129\",335559740,\"240\",201341983,\"0\",335559739,\"0\",201342446,\"1\",201342447,\"5\",201342448,\"3\",201342449,\"1\",201341986,\"1\",469775450,\"p4\",201340122,\"2\",134233614,\"true\",469778129,\"p4\",335572020,\"1\",134233118,\"true\",134233117,\"true\",469778324,\"Normal\"]}'\u003eNow, in our refreshed Honeysticks look – welcome to a world of pure creation!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"EOP SCXW59908151 BCX8\" data-ccp-props='{\"134233117\":true,\"134233118\":true,\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":0,\"335559740\":240}'\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Honeysticks UK","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":56350550425981,"sku":"HBTUBFS2","price":34.95,"currency_code":"GBP","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0553\/5465\/4896\/files\/UBFS_2.png?v=1765228589"},{"product_id":"honeysticks-bubble-bath","title":"Honeysticks Bubble Bath Colour Mixing 3pk 220ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"SCXW85038921 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW85038921 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"SCXW267638514 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW267638514 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"EN-NZ\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-parastyle=\"p4\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBring colour mixing to the tub!\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"EN-NZ\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-parastyle=\"p4\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHoneysticks Bubble Bath Colour Mixing 3pk 220ml\u003c\/strong\u003e transforms bath time into a playful, hands-on experiment in colour and creativity. With three mixable colours and a plant-based formula, kids can create six vibrant shades – all while enjoying soft, super-foamy bubbles. Fun bee-shaped bottles add to the magic.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-props='{\"134233117\":true,\"134233118\":true,\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":0,\"335559740\":240}'\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"EN-NZ\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\" data-ccp-charstyle-defn='{\"ObjectId\":\"65adc4b8-9fe6-5d96-a288-b4732a2d40b3|1\",\"ClassId\":1073872969,\"Properties\":[201342446,\"1\",201342447,\"5\",201342448,\"3\",201342449,\"1\",469777841,\"Cambria\",469777842,\"\",469777843,\"ＭＳ 明朝\",469777844,\"Cambria\",201341986,\"1\",469769226,\"Cambria,ＭＳ 明朝\",268442635,\"22\",469775450,\"s1\",201340122,\"1\",134233614,\"true\",469778129,\"s1\",335572020,\"1\",469778324,\"Default Paragraph Font\"]}'\u003eThree colours, six shades to explore:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"EN-NZ\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003e Includes red, yellow, and blue bottles – little creators can use them solo or mix to make a rainbow of six \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003epossible shades\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003e.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-props='{\"134233117\":true,\"134233118\":true,\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":0,\"335559740\":240}'\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003eSuper-foaming, naturally: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"EN-NZ\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003eSwirl under warm running water to whip up soft, fluffy bubbles and bring bath-time to life! Made with plant-based ingredients and cosmetic-grade pigments – no parabens, phthalates, or synthetic fragrances.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-props='{\"134233117\":true,\"134233118\":true,\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":0,\"335559740\":240}' style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003eFun bee-shaped bottles, planet-friendly packaging: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"EN-NZ\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003eEach 220ml bottle is made from 100% reclaimed plastic and packed in recyclable, PEFC-certified cardboard. Designed for little hands and big imaginations.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-props='{\"134233117\":true,\"134233118\":true,\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":0,\"335559740\":240}' style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003eSafe for children 1+: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"EN-NZ\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003eOur gentle, plant-based formula is rigorously safety tested for little creators aged 12 months and up. Made without SLS, parabens, phthalates, or synthetic fragrances. Colour comes from cosmetic and food-grade pigments.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-props='{\"134233117\":true,\"134233118\":true,\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":0,\"335559740\":240}' style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSo easy to clean up:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"EN-NZ\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003eSimply rinse the colourful water and bubbles down the drain – no stains on skin or bathroom surfaces.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-props='{\"134233117\":true,\"134233118\":true,\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":0,\"335559740\":240}' style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-charstyle=\"s1\"\u003eDesigned by parents who believe in a better way to play:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"EN-NZ\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-parastyle=\"p1\" data-ccp-parastyle-defn='{\"ObjectId\":\"5608de39-acc8-52c5-8723-06e2503f1031|1\",\"ClassId\":1073872969,\"Properties\":[469777841,\"Times New Roman\",469777842,\"Times New Roman\",469777843,\"Times New Roman\",469777844,\"Times New Roman\",469769226,\"Times New Roman\",268442635,\"24\",335559705,\"2057\",335551547,\"5129\",335559740,\"240\",201341983,\"0\",335559739,\"0\",201342446,\"1\",201342447,\"5\",201342448,\"3\",201342449,\"1\",201341986,\"1\",469775450,\"p1\",201340122,\"2\",134233614,\"true\",469778129,\"p1\",335572020,\"1\",134233118,\"true\",134233117,\"true\",469778324,\"Normal\"]}'\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c\/strong\u003eAt Honeysticks, we create safe, sustainable tools that inspire creativity and care for the world \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-parastyle=\"p1\"\u003ethey’ll\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-parastyle=\"p1\"\u003e grow up in.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-ccp-props='{\"134233117\":true,\"134233118\":true,\"201341983\":0